title: PRESS RELEASE- - Gent Sejko, Governor of the Bank of Albania attends 2015 Annual Meetings ...
text: ( Source : Bank of Albania ) Publication Date 13.10. 2015 On 9-11 October 2015 , Gent Sejko, Governor of the Bank of Albania, in capacity of the Governor of the Republic of Albania in IMF , attended the 2015 Annual Meetings of the World Bank
